{"type":null,"faqId":11290,"title":"Mate2 (MT2-L05) 后台播放与退出音乐，歌词同步","answer":"<p style=\"margin-left:63.8pt;text-indent:-13.9pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">后台播放：进入</span><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">“</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">音乐</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">”</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">播放器</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">播放任意音频文件</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">播放过程中按</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">Back</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">或</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">Home</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">键。</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:63.8pt;text-indent:-13.9pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">退出音乐：在音乐播放界面，点击手机</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">Menu</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">键，选择退出，在弹出的框上选择确定，即可退出</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">“</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">音乐</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">”</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">应用。</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"></span> \n</p>\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">歌词同步：当歌曲和对应的歌词存储在手机同一目录时，用户播放这首歌曲，歌词会自动加载。在播放界面，点击播放进度条上方的小三角按钮，可以打开歌词界面。在歌词界面，点击歌词，在界面会有两个按钮</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">“</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">延迟</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">秒</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">”</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">、</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">“</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">快进</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">秒</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">”</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">，分别会将歌词延迟</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">秒和快进</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">秒。</span>","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2050","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1398215574000,"seriesProductName":"MT2-L05","visitedTimes":6,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"Mate2 (MT2-L05)","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}